divs: sighting detailsmy sister and i were enjoying the beautiful night this past friday and were outside in my backyard. behind us are woods, or a full section of land that is not occupied by homes. we were talking and a brilliant white object that was pulsating red caught my eye. it was in the tree line, but off to a distance, say 1\4 mile away. it was wobbly, but moved up and down and side to side. it moved in a way normal aircraft cannot. what struck my attention is the red, pulsating lights. it was more like a strobe light going from brilliant white to red.
